## 6) Operational defaults

- Graceful shutdown: `await worker.close()` with termination grace period >= max job heartbeat window.
- Health endpoints reflect Redis connectivity + event loop lag.
- Alert when bulk waiting count grows while critical SLA degrades (indicates shared bottleneck).

